lead_paragraph: Barcelona are on the verge of completing a reported 30 million euro (25.62 million pounds) move for Spain international Paco Alcacer from Valencia after the striker arrived for a medical with the La Liga champions on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Alcacer Has Barcelona Medical Ahead of Proposed Move
headline.main: Alcacer Has Barcelona Medical Ahead of Proposed Move
